Fix an error with an 8 or larger vector result (#5817)

If using the formula modulator and returning all 8 vector
slots, Surge will crash and hang. This is due to two reasons.
1: Lua and its damn 1 based indexing. Sigh. But also
2: A bad condition not marking the function as invalid so an error loop

This fixes both